oiler safe up to 572°F, ceramics can also be used in the microwave and are dishwasher safe. Highly scratch and impact-resistant, Staub ceramics are conveniently freezer safe. Features      Transitions from oven to table beautifully     The set included: 7. 5\" X 6\" And 10. 5\" X 7. 5\" Rectangular baking dishes for making casseroles, lasagna, and more     Designed by Staub in France. Vitreous glass porcelain-enamel finish.     Stoneware will not absorb moisture, diffuses heat gently, and retains heat exceptionally well',50,0,0,14,'[]','[]','Kitchen'),(72,'Rainforest Cooking Ladle','Rainforest-BowlsWood-Cooking-Ladle','https://res.cloudinary.com/dr6yye7b1/image/upload/v1710862640/uxyosfpkft2ew6myeyi2.webp','Rainforest bowels',NULL,'Description Features      Made of sturdy Javanese teak wood, sustainably harvested from regulated plantations     Hand-carved by artisans in Central Java and Bali, Indonesia     Can be used with warm and cold drinks     Coated with beeswax and natural food-grade oil     Safe to use with food     Easy to wash and clean  What\'s Included?      1 Cooking Ladle(s)  About This Product  What\'s Included:1 Teak Wood Soup Cooking Serving LadleMade with 100% teak wood, this wooden ladle works like a charm. It has a long, slender handle that’s easy to grip as you stir and mix your ingredients. Its surface is covered in golden brown tones and lovely grain patterns you won’t find in any other hardwoods. It offers a stylish look without sacrificing functionality in the kitchen.Teak wood is especially perfect for kitchen settings. Teak is known to be highly resistant to moisture-related damage and rot, making this 7.5-inch wooden ladle ideal for serving soups, stews, and pasta sauces. In terms of longevity, the beeswax and natural mineral oils used to coat this spoon adds a layer of protection against wear and tear, heat, and rot. It also adds a wonderful sheen to the spoon that highlights its rustic textures. Use this spoon freely without worrying it 